videos.headline: KCP elevates for tough and-1 finish

videos.description: Jimmy Butler and Dwight Howard have to be separated after getting tangled up under the basket.

videos.headline: Howard, Butler receive double technicals after getting into it

videos.description: On the fast break, LeBron James throws an alley-oop to Anthony Davis, who rises up to throw down a dunk with reckless abandon.

videos.headline: LeBron sets up AD for tomahawk jam

videos.description: On a rebound attempt, Anthony Davis appears to injure his lower right leg and goes down to the ground in pain.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD goes down with a leg injury in the 1st quarter) 2020/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD goes down with a leg injury in the 1st quarter

videos.description: Kendrick Nunn makes a wraparound pass to Jimmy Butler, who goes up and into Anthony Davis to draw the foul and sink the bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler draws and-1 on AD) 2020/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler draws and-1 on AD

videos.description: LeBron James pulls up for his third 3-pointer of the first half to cut into the Heat's lead.
videos.headline: LeBron swishes 3

videos.description: LeBron James powers through the lane for the transition layup and gets fouled in the process.
videos.headline: LeBron muscles in and-1 bucket

videos.description: Jimmy Butler pulls up for a 3-pointer as the shot clock sounds to close out the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler beats shot clock with 3 to end half) 2020/10/9

videos.headline: Butler beats shot clock with 3 to end half

videos.description: Jimmy Butler goes up to get the second chance bucket and gets whacked across the face by Dwight Howard.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Butler gets whacked by Howard on and-1) 2020/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Butler gets whacked by Howard on and-1

videos.description: Jae Crowder drains a 3-pointer while being fouled.
videos.headline: Crowder fired up after 4-point play

videos.description: Duncan Robinson sinks the 3-pointer as Kyle Kuzma recklessly goes crashing into him to send him to the line.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Robinson sinks and-1 3-pointer with Kuzma crashing into him) 2020/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Robinson sinks and-1 3-pointer with Kuzma crashing into him

videos.description: LeBron James passes to an open Kentavious Caldwell-Pope, who drains a 3-pointer to give the Lakers a 97-96 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KCP drains a 3 as Lakers' regain the lead) 2020/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: KCP drains a 3 as Lakers' regain the lead

videos.description: LeBron James puts up the layup, but is blocked by Jimmy Butler.
videos.headline: Butler denies LeBron

videos.description: With the shot clock winding down, Anthony Davis gets the ball under the bucket and lays it in to put the Lakers up by 1 with under 30 seconds to go.
videos.headline: AD lays in go-ahead bucket

videos.description: LeBron James passes out to Danny Green, who misses a potential game-winning shot, then Markieff Morris tosses the ball out of bounds as the Lakers falter late in Game 5.
videos.headline: Lakers botch crucial possession

videos.description: Jimmy Butler speaks with Rachel Nichols after the Heat's win over the Lakers and commends Duncan Robinson's big game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Butler praises Robinson's Game 5 performance) 2020/10/9

videos.headline: Butler praises Robinson's Game 5 performance
